{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/melinnie-angela-memberi-warna-pada-chammyland/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Melinnie Angela Memberi Warna Pada Chammyland","content":"<p>Selalu ada momen pertama kali untuk mencoba sesuatu. Hal ini juga dialami sama Melinnie Angela. Meski udah suka bikin komik dari kecil, cewek pecinta anjing ini belum pernah menggeluti dunia komik secara profesional. <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/comic/chammyland\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Chammyland</a> adalah pengalaman pertamanya di dunia komik. <strong>Maria Megayanti (MM)</strong> dari CIAYO Blog sempet ngobrol-ngobrol santai sama <strong>Melinnie Angela (MA)</strong>, sang <em>colorist </em>Chammyland. Yuk, kenalan lebih deket sama cewek imut ini.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_3350\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3350\" data-attachment-id=\"3350\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/melinnie-angela-memberi-warna-pada-chammyland/attachment/body8-12/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body8-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Groovy Estate &#8211; Chammyland (ciayo.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Groovy Estate &#8211; Chammyland (ciayo.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body8-4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body8-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3350\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body8-4.jpg\" alt=\"Groovy Estate - Chammyland (ciayo.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body8-4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body8-4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3350\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Groovy Estate &#8211; Chammyland (ciayo.com)</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>MM: Sejak kapan suka gambar?</strong></p>\n<p>MA: Gua dari SD sih, soalnya kakak gua suka gambar. Terus gua ikut-ikutan gambar, sampe sekarang kerja demennya gambar.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_3332\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3332\" data-attachment-id=\"3332\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/melinnie-angela-memberi-warna-pada-chammyland/attachment/body2-21/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-10.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Melinnie\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Duh, senyumnya manis banget deh :) (CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-10-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-10.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3332\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-10.jpg\" alt=\"Duh, senyumnya manis banget deh :) (CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-10.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-10-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3332\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Duh, senyumnya manis banget deh ðŸ™‚ (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>MM: Dulu suka ikut lomba-lomba gambar gitu nggak?</strong></p>\n<p>MA: Dulu sih pas dari TK, SD, bahkan sampe SMP suka ikut lomba-lomba. SMA juga ngambilnya <em>art</em>. Jadi dari dulu emang pengennya ke arah situ.</p>\n<p><strong>MM: Pas awal-awal suka gambar, bikin ilustrasi apa? </strong></p>\n<p>MA: Gue suka gambar komik Jepang, suka baca komik Jepang. Tapi semenjak kuliah, lebih ke <em>western </em>sih. Lebih ke ilustrasi buat animasi barat.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_3344\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3344\" data-attachment-id=\"3344\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/melinnie-angela-memberi-warna-pada-chammyland/attachment/body6-17/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body6-6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Commision karya kanvas akrilik\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Commision karya kanvas akrilik&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body6-6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body6-6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3344\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body6-6.jpg\" alt=\"Commision karya kanvas akrilik\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body6-6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body6-6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3344\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Commision karya kanvas akrilik</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>MM: Ceritain dong, sebelum <em>join</em> di CIAYO Comics ngerjain apa? </strong></p>\n<p>MA: Sebelum di CIAYO, kerjaan gua bikin <em>childrenâ€™s book</em>. Ngerjain buat buku anak-anak, lebih ke ilustrasi. Belom pernah sama sekali ngerjain komik secara profesional. Jadi ini bener-bener <em>experience </em>baru banget dan belajar banyak juga.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_3341\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3341\" data-attachment-id=\"3341\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/melinnie-angela-memberi-warna-pada-chammyland/attachment/body5-20/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body5-7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Personal project character design Madam Helga\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Personal project character design Madam Helga&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body5-7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body5-7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3341\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body5-7.jpg\" alt=\"Personal project character design Madam Helga\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body5-7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body5-7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3341\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Personal project character design Madam Helga</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>MM: Kalo sekarang kan jadi <em>colorist </em>nya Chammyland ya. <em>Next </em>nya, pengen bikin komik sendiri juga nggak?</strong></p>\n<p>MA: Pengen sih. Soalnya kalo sekarang kan kerjaannya Fahmi yang gambar, gua yang ngewarnain. Pengen kalo ada kesempatan buat bener-bener gambar gua sendiri, ide gua sendiri, dan <em>style </em>gua sendiri. Mungkin <em>one shot</em> dulu ya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_3338\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3338\" data-attachment-id=\"3338\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/melinnie-angela-memberi-warna-pada-chammyland/attachment/body4-20/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body4-8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Chammyland (ciayo.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Chammyland (ciayo.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body4-8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body4-8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3338\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body4-8.jpg\" alt=\"Chammyland (ciayo.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body4-8.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body4-8-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3338\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Chammyland (ciayo.com)</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>MM: Melinnie hobinya apa sih? Masih suka baca komik nggak?</strong></p>\n<p>MA: Baca komik sekarang udah jarang. Hobi, apa yahâ€¦ya paling gambar, nonton film, maen sama anjing di rumah.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_3347\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3347\" data-attachment-id=\"3347\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/melinnie-angela-memberi-warna-pada-chammyland/attachment/body7-14/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body7-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Guguk pug bikinan Melinnie\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Guguk pug bikinan Melinnie&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body7-4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body7-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3347\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body7-4.jpg\" alt=\"Guguk pug bikinan Melinnie\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body7-4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body7-4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3347\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Guguk pug bikinan Melinnie</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_3353\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3353\" data-attachment-id=\"3353\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/melinnie-angela-memberi-warna-pada-chammyland/attachment/body10-10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body10-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Kalo lagi senggang, Melinnie leyeh-leyeh di ruang santai\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Kalo lagi senggang, Melinnie leyeh-leyeh di ruang santai (CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body10-3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body10-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3353\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body10-3.jpg\" alt=\"Kalo lagi senggang, Melinnie leyeh-leyeh di ruang santai (CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body10-3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body10-3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3353\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kalo lagi senggang, Melinnie leyeh-leyeh di ruang santai (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>MM: Suka film apa?</strong></p>\n<p>MA: Banyak sih. Marvel, DC suka. Apapun gua tonton sih, asal ceritanya menarik. Mau itu horor, komedi, drama, <em>romance, </em>asal ceritanya menarik. Film lokal juga gua tonton.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_3329\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3329\" data-attachment-id=\"3329\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/melinnie-angela-memberi-warna-pada-chammyland/attachment/body1-22/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body1-10.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Serius bener, Mel&#8230;\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Serius bener, Mel&#8230;(CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body1-10-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body1-10.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3329\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body1-10.jpg\" alt=\"Serius bener, Mel...(CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body1-10.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body1-10-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3329\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Serius bener, Mel&#8230;(CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>MM: Film apa yang terakhir ditonton dan suka sama jalan ceritanya?</strong></p>\n<p>MA: Into the Wild. Itu film lama, tapi gua baru nonton. Itu kan filmnya tentang jalan-jalan. Gua juga suka jalan-jalan, terus dapet banyak pelajaran dari film itu.</p>\n<p><strong>MM: Kesulitan ato tantangan apa yang dihadapi selama kerja?</strong></p>\n<p>MA: Mungkin<em> deadline, </em>nggak bisa diundur. Soalnya ngerjain komik emang harus gitu kan. Jadi kalo misalnya gua absen, sakit, ato hari libur, tetep harus selesai. Tapi emang harusnya begitu. Dulu sih sempet <em>struggle </em>soalnya masih adaptasi, apalagi <em>chapter-chapter </em>awal. Sekarang sih udah ketemu <em>method </em>sendiri yang lebih cepet. Jadi udah lumayan oke.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_3335\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3335\" data-attachment-id=\"3335\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/melinnie-angela-memberi-warna-pada-chammyland/attachment/body3-18/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body3-8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Kesibukan Melinnie di kantor\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Kesibukan Melinnie di kantor (CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body3-8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body3-8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3335\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body3-8.jpg\" alt=\"Kesibukan Melinnie di kantor (CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body3-8.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body3-8-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3335\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kesibukan Melinnie di kantor (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>MM: Mimpi apa yang pengen Melinnie capai? (Heheâ€¦berat banget, sis bahas mimpi! ðŸ˜€ )</strong></p>\n<p>MA: Gua pengen buka toko sendiri, buat jualan <em>merchandise. </em>Tapi ilustrasinya hasil karya gua. Sama pengen <em>release </em>buku cerita anak.</p>\n<p><strong>MM: Film Disney apa yang paling Kamu suka?</strong></p>\n<p>MA: Lion King</p>\n<p><strong>MM: Film Indonesia yang paling Kamu suka?</strong></p>\n<p>MA: Film Indonesia? AADC kali yahâ€¦</p>\n<p><strong>MM: Princess yang paling Kamu suka?</strong></p>\n<p>MA: Moana</p>\n<p><strong>MM: Siapa yang cukup menginspirasi karya-karya Kamu selama ini?</strong></p>\n<p>MA: Banyak banget. Tapi yang paling gua suka namanya Lorelay Bove, dia <em>concept artist </em>di Disney, orang Spanyol.</p>\n<p><strong>MM: Pernah belajar bahasa asing selain bahasa Inggris nggak?</strong></p>\n<p>MA: Waktu itu pernah nyoba belajar bahasa Perancis sih. Ngambil kelas satu semester pas kuliah.</p>\n<p><strong>MM: Skill lain apa yang pengen Kamu gali dan pelajari?</strong></p>\n<p>MA: Mungkin pengen bisa animasi kali yah. <em>Traditional painting</em> juga pengen digali lagi.</p>\n<p><strong>MM: Komik menurut Kamu tuh apa sih?</strong></p>\n<p>MA: Komik itu menurut gua samaÂ seperti <em>art </em><em>â€‹form</em>â€‹ yang lain (musik, film, painting, etc). <em>Itâ€™s all about storytelling.</em><em> Â </em></p>\n<p><strong>MM: Ada pesan-pesan nggak buat temen-temen yang lagi belajar dan baru terjun ke dunia komik? </strong></p>\n<p>MA: Jangan berkecil hati atau minder kalo ngeliat kerjaan orang lain yang lebih bagus dari kalian, <em>because all the good artist out ther</em>e juga dulu mulai dari posisi yang sama seperti kalian kok.â€‹ <em>Keep doing </em><em>what you&#8217;re doing!â€‹</em></p>\n<p>Apapun pekerjaannya, kalo dijalani sepenuh hati dan bersungguh-sungguh pasti berkah deh. Makasih udah mampir, bro sis! Sampe jumpa di Chit Chat selanjutnya bareng <em>artist-artist</em> yang nggak kalah kece.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"af10887d-4cea-53cf-8f61-e77b5a372ff9"}}}